<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THE ENDEAVOUR BAND</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kristien lawihaw, gamla naia,
 I kikhawm Krista thusin di'n;
 A thu sim hitiu, a tien cheng,
 Kinep leh kipahna'n a dim.

[V2]
 Ei haw Kristien lawihaw, A minin kikhawm leng,
 I lungtup kibangin, A min phuongzak hitiu;
 Dettak in ding hitiu, Pathien leh I gam di'n,
 Kristien lawihaw ei venna dingin paucham un.

[V3]
 2. I kikhawm zien mitin in Lal,
 Krista chawihatna lasa di'n;
 Kumsawt a hin tawplo lampi,
 Khangthak ten a muh theih na'ng un.

[V4]
 3. I Lapau na sem zel hitiu,
 Sem zing di'n kisa zel hitiu;
 A nung zuia, Amah ging di'n,
 Van Ina I kikhawp chan un.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>429</hymn_number>
</song>